::Zardus::

Zardus looks Feline over, nodding. "I think you'll find the mission itself to 
your liking," he says, glancing down at her hand on his chest, "If not, 
however, I could arrange some sort of ... reward," his eyes slide from her 
pelvic area up to her neck. Zardus looks back at Feline's face, "The mission 
will r-"

Zardus is interrupted as Dark One makes his entrance, raising an eyebrow as 
he nearly pushes her out of her chair. Zardus stands up, looking at Feline. 
"No, you'll be partnered with Skulletron. This is Dark One, leader of the 
Oblitercons."

He looks at Dark One. "Can you take your group and destroy the forest, oh 
maybe for a mile's radius?"
